---
By: Vladimir Solovyov
Source:
  ISBN: 978-1571746931
  Locus:
    Page: 102
  Title: The Essential Mystics, Poets, Saints and Sages
---
The light that comes with wisdom
turns time into a dream, and even
forces death to retreat.
The name of the eternal Beloved
hides within my heart,
yet I am a meek and timid lover.
